{"id":25293,"date":"2017-10-22T13:07:22","date_gmt":"2017-10-22T09:07:22","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=25293"},"modified":"2019-04-20T20:35:25","modified_gmt":"2019-04-20T16:35:25","slug":"when-the-prophet-forgot-ablution","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/when-the-prophet-forgot-ablution\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Prayer: When the Prophet forgot ablution for prayer"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The prayer had been prepared and the rows straightened, then the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to us. When he stood in his place of prayer, he remembered that he was in a state of ritual impurity (<em>junub<\/em>). The Prophet said to us, \u201c<strong>Stay in your place.<\/strong>\u201d Then, he went back inside to perform a ritual bath (<em>ghusl<\/em>) and then he came out to us with his hair dripping wet. The Prophet exalted Allah and we prayed with him.<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 271, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 605<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/em><\/strong> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064f\u0642\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064f\u062f\u0651\u0650\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064f\u0641\u064f\u0648\u0641\u064f \u0642\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644